textContent:
---happy 3rd---

3 months!! After everything we've been through, naka 3 months palang pala tayo bby?! AHHAHAAH CUTEEE!! It honestly just keeps getting better and better my love.

I want to thank you so much for everything we've been through this month! Mula sa pagsama and pagsuporta mo saken nung nabangga ako, sa pagpapakilala saken sa friends mo, pati na rin sa laging pag comfort saken any time na na mainsecure ako huhuhu. I just keep on realizing how lucky I really am to be with my bby!! I love you so much and I'm never ever letting you go!!

I'm so excited to see you tomorrow bby!! Maiintroduce ko narin yung jowa ko sa papa ko sa wakas!! Makikita na niya woman of my dreams ko! Yung babaeng papakasalan ko! I'm really proud of you my bby! I always am! There has never been a time na ayaw kong iflex ka. Kaya super excited talaga ako na iinteoduce ka bukas sa tatay ko, pati na rin sa tita ko! Marerealize na rin nila gaano ako kaswerte sa wakas!! Kase yung jowa ko, ang ganda na, ang talino pa, ang bait pa, tas super sweet pa oh ha! I love you so much Rei!! Happy 3rd Monthsary!
